This paper deals with natural language processing and information retrieval, which are the main topics of the sub-categories cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also uses machine learning techniques, which are covered in cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with data analysis and clustering, which are covered in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.CL and cs.IR, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.DS.
